imdb.plot outline: Three stages with live music, enjoyed the many visitors. Even Miss Lower Saxony 2011, Saskia Höfler, gave autographs. INSANE, one of the top-acts, was founded in November 2010: - Roger Reichert, guitar and vocals - Vincent Wüstefeld, guitar - Josephine Klein, bass and vocals - Rouven Reichert, drums and Clemens Damerau, keyboard (as a guest).
